{
  "stem": "26142.16",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were standing there for about two hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We couldn't-- you couldn't stand because these-- these Haftling clothings, those were linen, thin linen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was-- I think this killed more people than the hunger because they were not from the cold.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, we noticed-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all of a sudden, we noticed that in-- in front-- in front, by the entrance, was a-- a big Christmas tree, illuminated at the entrance.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And on the left side, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] an officer came in with four soldiers, walked out of the car, and here, all of a sudden, we noticed that there is a gallow, erected right at the front.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "From-- and-- and-- and it got dark already and it was all-- all illuminated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- the officers with the four soldiers that came in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They called out three numbers, the three numbers-- each one had-- they knew-- knew their number.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The three people and on the loudspeaker, they would read the-- the Haftling number, the Haftling name, and on the name of the Reichsfuhrer, Heinrich Himmler-- Himmler was from the-- from the SS.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Those Haftling number so-and-so is sentenced to death by hanging for trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Another one, that was-- another-- that was a Russian soldier, a Russian officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Another-- the other two were sentenced to hanging by-- by hitting back a Kapo-- that they were hitting back a Kapo.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And after each one was taken over, brought over-- hanged, the-- the poor guys, the poor guys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I remember, we were no more cold when we saw that, what's happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We were frozen numb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But they-- they yelled out, Hitler, Germany will pay for this!",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
